org.apache.river.mercury.proxy

Class ListenerProxy

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.river.mercury.proxy.ListenerProxy
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Remote, EventListener, net.jini.core.event.RemoteEventListener, net.jini.id.ReferentUuid

    public class ListenerProxy
extends Object
implements net.jini.core.event.RemoteEventListener, Serializable, net.jini.id.ReferentUuid
    The ListenerProxy class implements the RemoteEventListener interface. Instances of this class are provided as the event "forwarding" target to clients of the mailbox service.
    Since:
    1.1
